videos.description: Washington QB Jake Browning connects with Dante Pettis on a 32-yard pass, moving them to the Utah 40-yard line.
videos.headline: Pettis makes contested grab along sideline to move Huskies in Utah territory

videos.description: Washington RB Myles Gaskin gets the handoff and runs it in for the nine-yard touchdown. It was Gaskin's 38th career touchdown, a school record.
videos.headline: Gaskin puts Huskies on board with record TD

videos.description: Utah QB Tyler Huntley hits Raelon Singleton for a 40-yard touchdown pass and gives them a 7-6 lead.
videos.headline: Utah takes lead with 40-yard strike

videos.description: Utah kicker Mitch Wishnowsky recovers the onside kick attempt giving his team the ball on their own 48-yard line.
videos.headline: Utah kicker recovers own onside kick

videos.description: Washington safety JoJo McIntosh gets ejected for a big hit on Troy McCormick Jr.
videos.headline: Washington safety ejected for targeting

videos.description: Washington WR Dante Pettis runs for a 32-yard gain and sets up a Washington touchdown.
videos.headline: Pettis' long run sets up Huskies TD

videos.description: Washington QB Jake Browning hits Lavon Coleman for a six-yard touchdown pass and gives them a 13-10 lead.
videos.headline: Browning avoids rush, hits Coleman to give Huskies a touchdown

videos.description: Utah QB Tyler Huntley's pass is intercepted by Washington's Taylor Rapp and is returned to the Washington 40-yard line.
videos.headline: Utah QB's INT gives Huskies ball near midfield

videos.description: Utah QB Tyler Huntley connects with Demari Simpkins for the 31-yard pass, setting them up at the Washington nine-yard line.
videos.headline: Utah connects on deep ball moving them inside the 10-yard line

videos.description: Utah QB Tyler Huntley hooks up with Raelon Singleton for the 11-yard touchdown, giving them a 23-16 lead.
videos.headline: Utah takes back lead with TD pass

videos.description: Washington QB Jake Browning connects with Myles Gaskin for the 76-yard touchdown pass.
videos.headline: Washington answers with 76-yard TD to tie game

videos.description: Utah punter Mitch Wishnowsky runs 19 yards for the first down, but then is penalized 15 yards for spiking the ball in celebration.
videos.headline: Utah punter runs 19-yards for 1st down, loses 15  for spiking ball

videos.description: Utah QB Tyler Huntley sprints up the middle for the go-ahead, five-yard touchdown, giving the Utes a 30-23 lead.
videos.headline: Utah regains lead on the ground

videos.description: Washington QB Jake Browning gets hit and spins around in mid-air, but comes up short of the first down on his fourth down rush attempt.
videos.headline: Browning gets hit in mid-air, comes up short on 4th down scramble

videos.description: Washington RB Myles Gaskin gets the snap and runs up the middle for a two-yard, game-tying touchdown.
videos.headline: Late TD for Huskies' Gaskin knots score at 30

videos.description: Washington kicker Tristan Vizcaino kicks a game-winning 38-yard field goal as time expires.
videos.headline: Washington wins on 38-yard field goal

videos.description: Washington QB Jake Browning breaks down how Washington was able to come back against Utah.
videos.headline: Browning on comeback: 'We just started executing'
